# Singular-form redirects for category pages тАФ users naturally
# type `/oracle/`, `/dex/`, `/exchange/` etc. without the
# canonical plural. The 2026-05-08 audit confirmed all 9 below
# 404'd cold; bouncing each to its canonical plural eliminates
# the dead-end.
/oracle                        /oracles/      301
/oracle/                       /oracles/      301
/exchange                      /exchanges/    301
/exchange/                     /exchanges/    301
/dex                           /dexes/        301
/dex/                          /dexes/        301

# Aggregator-family aliases тАФ `/aggregators/` covers both routers
